name: Bajaj Pulsar NS160
details: The Pulsar NS160 was Bajaj’s response to the growing 160cc streetfighter segment. It carries over its bigger sibling, the Pulsar NS200’s styling and comes in a smaller-engined package offering a balance of performance and efficiency.
